## TAB CONFIG ##

faction-list:
  format: "&7%number%. %faction_name% &7[%faction_online_member%/%faction_max_member%] %faction_dtr_color%%faction_actual_dtr%%faction_dtr_symbol%"

faction:
  faction_info: "&bFaction Info" # %faction_info%
  name: "&fName: %name%" # %faction_name%
  leader: "&fLeader: %leader%" # %faction_leader%
  dtr: "&fDTR: %dtr%" # %faction_dtr%
  home: "&fHome: &c%home%" # %faction_home%
  points: "&fPoints: %points%" # %faction_points%
  balance: "&fBalance: %balance%" # %faction_balance%
  online: "&fOnline: %online%" # %faction_online%
  members: "&bMembers" # %faction_online%

no-faction:
  faction_info: "&bFaction Info"
  name: "&fName: None"
  leader: "&fLeader: None"
  dtr: "&fDTR: 0"
  home: "&fHome: &cNone"
  points: "&fPoints: 0"
  balance: "&fBalance: 0"
  online: "&fOnline: 0"
  members: ""

event:
  name: "&9&l%event%&7: "
  time: "&c%timer%"
  coords: "&7%x%, %z%"

  info:
    next-koth: "&bNext Koth"
    current-koth: "&bCurrent KoTH"

  schedule:
    empty: "&fNone Schedule"
    name: "%schedule_name%"
    time: "&f%schedule_time%"

tab:
  enabled: true
  header:
    - ""
    - "%title%"
    - "%footer%"
    - ""

  footer:
    - ""
    - "&fThere are &b%online_players% &fplayers in the network."
    - ""

  ping: 1 # You can set the ping of the tablist

  left:
    1: ""
    2: ""
    3: ""
    4: "<skin:stats>&bYour Statistcs"
    5: "&fKills: &a%player_kills%"
    6: "&fDeaths: &4%player_deaths%"
    7: "&fBalance: &e$%player_balance%"
    8: "&fLives: &c%player_lives%"
    9: "&fReputation: &d%player_reputation%"
    10: ""
    11: "<skin:earth>&bLocation"
    12: "&f%player_location_x%, %player_location_z% (%player_location_direction%)"
    13: "%faction_location%"
    14: ""
    15: "<skin:ping>&bYour Ping"
    16: "<player-ping>&f%player_ping%ms"
    17: ""
    18: ""
    19: ""
    20: ""
  middle:
    1: ""
    2: "<skin:aqua>&b&lVoid"
    3: "&f&ohelydev.com"
    4: ""
    5: ""
    6: "<faction-skin>%faction_info%"
    7: "%faction_name%"
    8: "%faction_leader%"
    9: "%faction_dtr%"
    10: "%faction_balance%"
    11: "%faction_points%"
    12: "%faction_online%"
    13: ""
    14: "%faction_members%"
    15: "%f_member_1%"
    16: "%f_member_2%"
    17: "%f_member_3%"
    18: "%f_member_4%"
    19: "%f_member_5%"
    20: "%f_member_6%"
  right:
    1: ""
    2: ""
    3: ""
    4: "<skin:ender_portal>&bEnd Portals"
    5: "&f1000, 1000"
    6: "&fin each quadrant"
    7: ""
    8: "<skin:bow>&bKit"
    9: "&fProt 1, Sharp 1"
    10: ""
    11: "<skin:deny>&bBorder"
    12: "&f1000x1000"
    13: ""
    14: "<skin:online_player>&bOnline"
    15: "&f%online_players%"
    16: ""
    17: "<skin:castle>%event-info%"
    18: "%event-name%%event-time%"
    19: "%event-coords%"
